{"SURSANURE":[{"def":"A wound healed or healing outwardly only.","pos":""}],"SURSOLID":[{"def":"The fifth power of a number; as, a is the sursolid of a, or 32 that of 2.","pos":""}],"SURSUM CORDA":[{"def":"In the Eucharist, the versicles immediately before the preface, inviting the people to join in the service by \"lifting up the heart\" to God.","pos":""}]}